#imprting requied libraries.
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import seaborn as sns #visualsation
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt #visualsation
%matplotlib inline
sns.set(color_codes=True)

x=np.linspace(0,10,100)

fig = plt.figure()
plt.plot(x, np.sin(x),  '-')
plt.plot(x, np.cos(x), '--')
